      • protoBuf

        public static final <M extends Message> ChannelInitializer<Channel> protoBuf(M defaultInstance,
                                                       SimpleChannelInboundHandler<M> handler)
        Returns a new channel initializer suited to encode and decode a protocol buffer message.

        Message sizes over 10 MB are not supported.

        The handler will be executed on the I/O thread. Blocking operations should be executed in their own thread.

        Type Parameters:
        M - the type of the support protocol buffer message
        Parameters:
        defaultInstance - an instance of the message to handle
        handler - the handler implementing the application logic

      • secureHttpServer

        public static final ChannelInitializer<Channel> secureHttpServer(SimpleChannelInboundHandler<HttpRequest> handler,
                                           SSLContext sslContext)
        Returns a server-side channel initializer capable of securely receiving and sending HTTP requests and responses

        Communications will be encrypted as per the configured SSL context

        Parameters:
        handler - the handler implementing the business logic.
        sslContext - the SSL context which drives the security of the link to the client.
